articles.author: Silvia Amaro
articles.title: Europe praises Trump's victory amid wider fears of an impending economic nightmare - CNBC
articles.description: European leaders are congratulating Donald Trump for his victory, while sources add the outcome is not as shocking as when he clinched victory in 2016.
articles.content:
